{"tid":429850,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解近年咁多人二十幾歲就結婚？","createTime":"2017-10-09T10:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T08:19:41.000Z","uid":63913,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc84c368009cf78228bb64092ec9e2b2a707924","tid":429850,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"以前70後同80年代頭出生的大多會於30歲打後先結婚，甚至好多會覺得35歲先係適婚年齡。到左近幾年，不少80年代尾出生的同90後一到左25歲左右就結婚。<br />\n<br />\n唔算奉子成緍，照計近十年多左人讀大學，即大家都遲左幾年先打工搵錢，甚至有人要於投身社會後幾年就重返校園進修。再加上樓價高、生活成本上升等等因素，結婚生子之事理應比70後的一代更困難，但點解事實卻是相反？"},{"pid":"d29202bea99d894379dc273448b35b03991ce83f","tid":429850,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aeffc8ed03be610d999f5bed4a9cfab4f6673a3","tid":429850,"uid":54951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔覺得遲婚直頭係個問題？"},{"pid":"892594f81c11e6f77bb57f87dcc018973edc9bd2","tid":429850,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"386b7200f519021976d529bcdbfd527cc5eb0587","tid":429850,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"父幹囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c304938f852d7b8f347fbb52d8a1359e80b433c","tid":429850,"uid":80761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"以前個代二十幾歲結婚先係正常啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7aa225c43879a1543bedd790a8a6de07ff5eea","tid":429850,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae56233a4d8673eb1a8f17ddafa1da980cef7768","tid":429850,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"1:父幹<br />\n2:新移民風氣，大陸人興早婚"},{"pid":"54